OL,6,FA hospital visitor was run over and
OL,7,Fkilled by a friend he was trying to
OL,8,Fhelp reverse into a parking space in a
OL,9,Fmulti-storey car park, a coroner heard
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FRichard Burton, 58, was visiting a
OL,13,Fpatient at the Royal Berkshire
OL,14,FHospital in Reading on 13 March when
OL,15,Fhe was fatally crushed under the
OL,16,Fwheels of a 44 vehicle.
