OL,6,FThe assistant coroner heard the driver
OL,7,Fof the vehicle lost control as he
OL,8,Ftried to reverse - lurching backwards
OL,9,Finto Mr Burton.JMr Burton, from
OL,10,FShirley Avenue, Reading, was killed on
OL,11,Flevel one of the multi-storey car park
OL,12,Fat the hospital last month.
OL,14,FHe had gone to the hospital to visit a
OL,15,Ffriend when he was accidentally run
OL,16,Fover by a reversing Mitsubishi 44 SUV.
