OL,6,FThames Valley Police launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation which is still ongoing
OL,8,Fand whose outcome will determine
OL,9,Fwhether an inquest is to take place,
OL,10,FMr Wade told the hearing.JHe said:
OL,11,F"This is a matter which, of course,
OL,12,Fcontinues to be investigated by Thames
OL,13,FValley Police. It is not exactly known
OL,14,Fwhat the outcome of their
OL,15,Finvestigation will be.J"However, the
OL,16,Fdeath is clearly unnatural, and an
OL,17,Finquest may be required at a later
OL,18,Fdate.J"This inquest is opened and
OL,19,Fadjourned.J"I will await to hear the
OL,20,Foutcome of the police investigation to
OL,21,Ffix an inquest date."JA later post-
OL,22,Fmortem examination gave the cause of
OL,23,FMr Burton's death as "multiple
OL,24,Finjuries."
